        public Train(String name,
     BigDecimal length,
     BigDecimal speedMultiplier,
     int tob,
     Node origin,
     Node destination,
     int entryTime,
     int wantTime,
     int originalScheduleAdherence,
     List<ScheduleAdherenceRequirement> sars,
     boolean hazmat,
     boolean isWestbound)
        Create new instance.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the train, must be in the format of [A-F][0-9]+. Will be used to determine the Train.Type.
        length - Length of the train in miles.
        speedMultiplier -
        tob - Tons per operative break. Will be used to determine train heaviness.
        origin - Where the train enters the Territory.
        destination - Where the train leaves the Territory.
        entryTime - Time in minutes since the start of the planning horizon, when the train enters the Territory.
        wantTime - Terminal want time in minutes since the start of the planning horizon, as defined by the RAS problem description.
        originalScheduleAdherence -
        sars - Schedule adherence requirements.
        hazmat - Does the train carry hazardous materials?
        isWestbound - Is the train going west?
